				<p>While our team has deep experience within the healthcare system, we dont know everything ;) The last thing we want to do is to spend time and money making something that no one really needs or wants. Research is fundamental to our design and development process. We do a mix of observation, interviews and experience prototyping. Depending on the scope and type of project we are working with we can spend anywhere from an hour conversation to a week of full time experience within the context.</p>

				<p>If you have a problem area but dont know what to do to fix it, we can step in to do interviews and observation, develop insights and then produce a diverse array of solutions that could either inspire you or could be the solution. If you have a product or service but want to improve it - we can take it into the field, analyze and brainstorm around possible solutions. If you know what you want to make but aren't sure in what way to make it - we can develop fast prototypes that are built to explore one aspect of your project and bring them to the context you are working in so that you can have a better understanding of how to put your goods out there.</p>
